data.title: Districts and Subdistricts: Name Status Population Population Population
data.meta_description: Bangladesh.doc - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document lists the districts, subdistricts, and populations from census years 1991, 2001, and 2011 for several districts in Bangladesh. It begins with Bagerhat district and its subdistricts and populations. It then continues alphabetically listing other districts such as Bandarban, Barguna, Barisal, and their respective subdistricts and populations from the three census years.
